name: ToothBrushing
0:
”Alexa start tooth brushing”
”Alexa tell tooth brushing I want to brush my teeth”
”Alexa ask tooth brushing when should I change my toothbrush”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tooth brushing
des:
Let "Tooth Brushing" accompany you while you brush your teeth, the Skill tells you when and where to brush and entertains you with music in the meantime. 
Ask your questions about dental care or be reminded to buy a new toothbrush. Just say "Alexa start tooth brushing" to start.

Royalty free music from www.frametraxx.de
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
